<font color="yellow">Untuk segalanya... terima kasih.</font>

146
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,890
<font color="yellow">Dia merusak tasmu?</font>

147
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:20,330
<font color="yellow">Itu benar.</font>

148
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:22,930
<font color="yellow">Dia merobeknya seperti ini...</font>

149
00:10:23,090 --> 00:10:24,910
<font color="yellow">Dan dia juga memukul Gyun Woo?</font>

150
00:10:24,930 --> 00:10:26,360
<font color="yellow">Kurang tepat kalau memukul.</font>

151
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:27,860
<font color="yellow">Dia begini.</font>

152
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:30,260
<font color="yellow">Astaga. Aku kecewa padanya.</font>

153
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:33,640
<font color="yellow">- Aku ke toilet dulu, ya.
- Belum selesai.</font>

154
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:36,710
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah membuatkan dia makan siang,
tapi malah disuruh enyah.</font>

155
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:38,990
<font color="yellow">Dia juga menyuruhku tutup mulut
dan sadar tempatku.</font>

156
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:41,440
<font color="yellow">- Jelas dia sosiopat.
- Apa?</font>

157
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:44,740
<font color="yellow">Aku sangat membeci seseorang yang memperlakukan
wanita, lansia, dan binatang...</font>

158
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:47,660
<font color="yellow">... dengan buruk.
Han Se Ju melakukan semuanya.</font>

159
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,410
<font color="yellow">Sudah, 'kan? Aku ke toilet dulu.</font>

160
00:10:50,430 --> 00:10:51,460
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

161
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,740
<font color="yellow">Sosiopat itu terlalu ekstrim.</font>

162
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,660
<font color="yellow">Tapi dia kasar padamu.</font>

163
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,630
<font color="yellow">Dia hanya sulit didekati. Itu saja.</font>

164
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,760
<font color="yellow">Apa semacam pertahanan diri begitu, ya?</font>

165
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:02,070
<font color="yellow">Dia hanya tidak tahu cara berhadapan dengan orang lain.</font>

166
00:11:02,090 --> 00:11:03,910
<font color="yellow">Jika kau teliti,
dia tidak punya gejala sakit kejiwaan.</font>

167
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:06,430
<font color="yellow">Hei, kau apaan, sih?</font>

168
00:11:06,530 --> 00:11:09,130
<font color="yellow">Lalu aku harus berekspresi bagaimana?</font>

169
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:12,510
<font color="yellow">- Memang aku kenapa?
- Kau suka padanya, ya?</font>

170
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:14,270
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau seperti itu?</font>

171
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:17,610
<font color="yellow">Aku hanya bicara fakta,
itu saja.</font>

172
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:20,170
<font color="yellow">Lupakan.
Mulai sekarang, ingatlah.</font>

173
00:11:20,190 --> 00:11:21,430
<font color="yellow">Kau penggemar atau anti-fan?</font>

174
00:11:21,530 --> 00:11:24,730
<font color="yellow">Aku akan merespon sesuai jawabanmu,
lalu ke toilet.</font>

175
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:27,170
<font color="yellow">Beri aku waktu.
Aku perlu berpikir.</font>

176
00:11:27,190 --> 00:11:30,090
<font color="yellow">Berpikir, omong kosong!
Aku kebelet, nih!</font>

177
00:11:39,890 --> 00:11:41,190
<font color="yellow">Yoo-ssi?</font>

178
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,530
<font color="yellow">Kita bertemu lagi.</font>

179
